snippet.title: Draw My Life : Team Trees (Full story)
snippet.description: Draw My Life : Team Trees covers the full movement of #teamtrees , After Mr beast hit 20 Million subscribers, a reddit post came in saying “Petitions for Mr beast to plan 20 Million trees” .It was a joke at first but after seeing fans pushing the idea to save earth and defeat Morgz , Mr beast actually decided to plant 20 Million trees . On October 26, 2019, Mr beast uploaded a special Video. In that he explained the whole situation and announced that he will be planting 20 million trees.You can say Team trees was the biggest movement of YouTube to do something good to save humanity. Draw My Life : Team Trees covers the entire story of the events leading to the final moment when we actually managed to raise 20 Million dollars.

We still have a long way to go. We would need 1.2 trillion new trees to completely negate human pollution. In other words, we would need to plant 20 million trees 59 999 more times to reach that amount. That's about 156 trees per currently living human. Luckily, this might be possible if we build drones for planting trees rather than killing people.
https://www.eurekalert.org/pub_releases/2019-02/ez-pcc021119.php
https://www.fastcompany.com/90329982/these-tree-planting-drones-are-firing-seed-missiles-to-restore-the-worlds-forests
